{"__type":"$$EventMessageAiNode","id":"230c2c28-6073-4dea-8cf4-5e733638f4ac","ts":"2026-02-23T13:16:26.141+00:00","eventName":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","message":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","payload":{"executionId":"1257","nodeName":"OpenAI Chat Model1","workflowName":"AI Agent","nodeType":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","workflowId":"mDNZrkXUkBc4LvfU","msg":"{\"messages\":[\"System: Please classify the text provided by the user into one of the following categories: devices, chatting, and use the provided formatting instructions below. Don't explain, and only output the json.\\n\\tYou must format your output as a JSON value that adheres to a given \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance.\\n\\n\\\"JSON Schema\\\" is a declarative language that allows you to annotate and validate JSON documents.\\n\\nFor example, the example \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": {{\\\"description\\\": \\\"a list of test words\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\", \\\"items\\\": {{\\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\"}}}}}}, \\\"required\\\": [\\\"foo\\\"]}}}}\\nwould match an object with one required property, \\\"foo\\\". The \\\"type\\\" property specifies \\\"foo\\\" must be an \\\"array\\\", and the \\\"description\\\" property semantically describes it as \\\"a list of test words\\\". The items within \\\"foo\\\" must be strings.\\nThus, the object {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}} is a well-formatted instance of this example \\\"JSON Schema\\\". The object {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}}}} is not well-formatted.\\n\\nYour output will be parsed and type-checked according to the provided schema instance, so make sure all fields in your output match the schema exactly and there are no trailing commas!\\n\\nHere is the JSON Schema instance your output must adhere to. Include the enclosing markdown codeblock:\\n```json\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"devices\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"boolean\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Should be true if the input has category \\\\\\\"devices\\\\\\\" (description: actions needed to be done on doors, lights, windows, fan or alarm)\\\"},\\\"chatting\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"boolean\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Should be true if the input has category \\\\\\\"chatting\\\\\\\" (description: normal chatting)\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"devices\\\",\\\"chatting\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"$schema\\\":\\\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\\\"}\\n```\\n\\n\\tCategories are mutually exclusive, and only one can be true\\n\\tIf there is not a very fitting category, select none of the categories.\\nHuman: شغل مروحة الشفط و ولع نور اول دور و اطفي التاني\"],\"options\":{\"openai_api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"qwen25-7b-instruct.Q4_K_M.gguf\",\"temperature\":0.7,\"top_p\":1,\"timeout\":60000,\"max_retries\":2,\"configuration\":{\"baseURL\":\"http://ollama:8080/v1\",\"fetchOptions\":{}},\"model_kwargs\":{}},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\\"devices\\\":true,\\\"chatting\\\":false}\\n```\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":15,\"promptTokens\":463,\"totalTokens\":478}}}"}}
