nstance of this example \\\"JSON Schema\\\". The object {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}}}} is not well-formatted.\\n\\nYour output will be parsed and type-checked according to the provided schema instance, so make sure all fields in your output match the schema exactly and there are no trailing commas!\\n\\nHere is the JSON Schema instance your output must adhere to. Include the enclosing markdown codeblock:\\n```json\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"output\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"pattern\\\":\\\"^[\\\\\\\\u0600-\\\\\\\\u06FF\\\\\\\\u0750-\\\\\\\\u077F\\\\\\\\u08A0-\\\\\\\\u08FF\\\\\\\\s\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\r،؛؟!.\\\\\\\\-]+$\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"output\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"$schema\\\":\\\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\\\"}\\n```\\n\"],\"options\":{\"openai_api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"qwen25-7b-instruct.Q4_K_M.gguf\",\"temperature\":0.7,\"top_p\":1,\"timeout\":60000,\"max_retries\":2,\"configuration\":{\"baseURL\":\"http://ollama:8080/v1\",\"fetchOptions\":{}},\"model_kwargs\":{}},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\\"output\\\":\\\"تم تشغيل المروحة بنجاح\\\\nتم إشعال النور على الطابق الأول بنجاح\\\\nتم إطفاء النور على الطابق الثاني بنجاح\\\"}\\n```\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":49,\"promptTokens\":609,\"totalTokens\":658}}}"}}
